n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section class=\"hero\">\n            <h2>Embrace the Charm of Smart Living</h2>\n            <p>Bringing modern convenience to a timeless aesthetic. Control your home with elegant simplicity.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Our Philosophy</h2>\n            <p>We believe technology should enhance your life without disrupting your peace. Our smart home solutions are designed to blend seamlessly with a rustic charm, offering intuitive control and reliable performance. From managing your lighting to ensuring your comfort, we bring the future home, rooted in tradition.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Key Features</h2>\n            <div class=\"feature-grid\">\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Intelligent Lighting</h3>\n                    <p>Set the mood with customizable lighting scenes that evoke warmth and comfort.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Climate Control</h3>\n                    <p>Maintain the perfect temperature with smart thermostats that learn your preferences.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Security & Monitoring</h3>\n                    <p>Peace of mind with discreetly integrated security systems.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Voice Integration</h3>\n                    <p>Effortless control through simple voice commands.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Discover the Difference</h2>\n            <p>Experience a home that understands you. Our technology is crafted for ease of use, durability, and a beauty that complements your rustic-inspired living space.</p>\n            <a href=\"#contact\